    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!) and<strong> ginger</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to a paste</p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> with the <strong>sriracha</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>soy sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Stir it all together – this is your<strong> spicy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1592845241344-x200.jpg",
